record.title: ADJOURNMENT UNTIL MONDAY, FEBRUARY 12, 2007, AT 1 P.M.

speaking.paragraph: If there is no further business to come before the Senate today, I now ask unanimous consent that the Senate stand adjourned under the previous order.

record.narrative: There being no objection, the Senate, at 6:12 p.m., adjourned until Monday, February 12, 2007, at 1 p.m.
